checkboxHandler("nsfw2"); checkboxHandler("nsfw3"); checkboxHandler("nsfw"); function checkboxHandler(content) { let warn_content = "input#checkbox--warn-" + content; $(warn_content).on("click", function() { if (document.querySelector(warn_content).checked) { /* Ensure the content isn't already in the array. */ if (!variables().ft_warning.includes(content)) { variables().ft_warning.push(content); } } else { variables().ft_warning = variables().ft_warning.filter(v => v !== content); } Engine.show(); }); let disable_content = "input#checkbox--disable-" + content; $(disable_content).on("click", function() { if (document.querySelector(disable_content).checked) { /* Ensure the content isn't already in the array. */ if (!variables().ft_disable.includes(content)) { variables().ft_disable.push(content); } } else { variables().ft_disable = variables().ft_disable.filter(v => v !== content); } Engine.show(); }); }; >>
